 and regional variability of phytoplankton biomass in the Northeast Atlantic (1960-1995) (2001) ICES J Mar Sci, 58, pp. 3-49; (2001) FAO Yearbook. Fisheries Statistics: Capture Production Volume 88/1. FAO Fisheries Series No. 57, FAO Statistical Series, 88 (1), p. 159. , Rome: FAO; (2001) FAO Yearbook. Fisheries Statistics: Aquaculture Production Volume 88/2. FAO Fisheries Series No. 58, FAO Statistical Series, 88 (2), p. 160. , Rome: FAO; Ford, E., A contribution to our knowledge of the life-histories of the dogfishes landed at Plymouth (1921) J Mar Biol Assoc UK, 12, pp. 468-505; Fromentin, J.-M., Planque, B., Calanus and environment in the eastern North Atlantic. II. Influence of the North Atlantic Oscillation on C. finmarchicus and C. helgolandicus (1996) Mar Ecol Prog Ser, 134, pp. 111-118; Hiscock, K., Southward, A.J., Tittley, I., Jory, A., Hawkins, S.J., (2001) The Impact of Climate Change on Subtidal and Intertidal Benthic Species in Scotland, , Report to Scottish National Heritage from the Marine Biological Association of the United Kingdom - Final Report. Plymouth, UK: Marine Biological Association; Holme, N.A., The bottom fauna of the English Channel (1961) J Mar Biol Assoc UK, 41, pp. 397-461; Holme, N.A., Fluctuations in the benthos of the western English Channel (1983) Proceedings of the 17th European Symposium on Marine Biology, Oceanologica Acta, SPEC. VOL., pp. 121-124; Jakobsson, J., Monitoring and management of the northeast Atlantic herring stocks (1985) Can J Fish Aquat Sci, 42 (SUPPL. 1), pp. 207-221; Jennings, S., Kaiser, M.J., The effects of fishing on marine ecosystems (1998) Adv Mar Biol, 34, pp. 201-352; Jennings, S., Kaiser, M.J., Reynolds, J.D., (2000) Marine fisheries ecology, , Oxford: Blackwell Science; Jennings, S., Greenstreet, S.P.R., Reynolds, J.D., Structural change in an exploited fish community: A consequence of differential fishing effects on species with contrasting life histories (1999) J Anim Ecol, 68, pp. 617-627; Lamb, H